<plot>The Reel Life story of man's cold turkey detox from his 15 year addiction to heroin. Bryant 'HairKuTT' Johnson decided he had to get himself clean to gain custody of his daughter who's mother had just died. HairKuTT travels to a remote cabin in the Smoky Mountains of Tennessee and with the support of three friends he kicks his habit cold turkey in front of the camera.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?227234</url></doc>
